OL,3,CCold-case detectives offer reward on
OL,4,C30-year murder
OL,6,FCold-case detectives have offered a
OL,7,F#50,000 reward for information about
OL,8,Fthe murder of a man almost 30-years-
OL,9,Fago - to help his 85-year-old mother
OL,10,Ffinally come to terms with his death.
OL,12,FPaul McGrath was 34 when he was
OL,13,Fstabbed repeatedly after a night out
OL,14,Fin Greater Manchester on 6 April 1997.
OL,16,FHe had been for a drink with friends
OL,17,Fat the Dog and Partridge pub, on
OL,18,FAshton Road, in Ashton-under-Lyne, and
OL,19,Fafterwards went home alone.
