OL,6,FOfficers say they believe his killers
OL,7,Fwere searching for one of his
OL,8,Facquaintances when they arrived at his
OL,9,Fhouse just after midnight. He was
OL,10,Fattacked and stabbed 18 times in what
OL,11,Fpolice say, was a frenzied and
OL,12,Ftargeted attack.
OL,14,FMr McGrath's body was found by a
OL,15,Fpassing workman at 7.30am the
OL,16,Ffollowing day lying by the partially
OL,17,Fopen front door of his home on Holland
OL,18,FStreet West in Denton.
