OL,3,CCold-case detectives offer reward on
OL,4,C30-year murder
OL,6,FAccording to detectives Paul was well-
OL,7,Fliked and respected in the community,
OL,8,Fand had no known grievances, and they
OL,9,Fsay he was targeted after one of his
OL,10,Facquaintances became involved in an
OL,11,Fongoing dispute.
OL,13,FTwo men were arrested for his murder
OL,14,Fwithin two weeks, but were acquitted
OL,15,Fafter a lengthy trial.
