OL,3,CCold-case detectives offer reward on
OL,4,C30-year murder
OL,6,FDetective Constable Matthew Sharkey
OL,7,Ffrom Greater Manchester Police's Cold
OL,8,FCase Unit, said: "We know there are
OL,9,Fpeople out there who are able to tell
OL,10,Fus what they know and what they saw
OL,11,Fall those years ago.
OL,13,F"Although it was nearly 30 years ago,
OL,14,Fyou can't just forget what you saw, it
OL,15,Fwill be playing on the mind of someone
OL,16,Fwho knows something, and I hope their
OL,17,Fconscience will allow them to speak to
OL,18,Fus after all this time ` please come
OL,19,Fand tell us the truth.
