OL,3,CCold-case detectives offer reward on
OL,4,C30-year murder
OL,6,F"Your information could help a
OL,7,Fgrieving family know what happened to
OL,8,Ftheir beloved son and it is never too
OL,9,Flate to come forwards.
OL,11,F"All of the work we are doing is to
OL,12,Fget Vera, Paul's mother, to finally
OL,13,Fsee her son's killer or killers
OL,14,Fbrought to justice and help a family
OL,15,Ffinally come to terms with the death
OL,16,Fof their loved one."
OL,18,FPaul's sister Gillian is continuing to
OL,19,Furge people for their information, not
OL,20,Fjust for her but also for her elderly
OL,21,Fmother Vera who is 85-years-old.
