OL,3,CCold-case detectives offer reward on
OL,4,C30-year murder
OL,6,FShe said: "I saw my mum bury her son
OL,7,Fand it was the worst thing in the
OL,8,Fworld to witness.
OL,10,F"My mum, along with the rest of our
OL,11,Ffamily, goes to Paul's grave to lay
OL,12,Fflowers on his birthday every year and
OL,13,Fwe have done this for the last 27
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,F"We just wish that we knew exactly
OL,17,Fwhat happened to our Paul and see
OL,18,Fthose who brutally killed him to be
OL,19,Fbrought to justice."
